data.description: Priced to sell with the best yard and location in Santaquin! Boasting 6 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, formal and informal living and dining rooms on the main, and a massive family room in the basement. The home features crown molding, granite counter tops, hardwood floors, a beautiful fireplace and much more! Outdoor enthusiasts will love the mature, private, huge and fully fenced yard sharing a fence with only one neighbor on the right and a babbling brook on the left. You can even take walks to Santaquin Canyon from this home! Minutes from easy freeway access - this is a home you won't want to miss. The seller may be willing to negotiate seller paid concessions for new carpet with the right offer. Square footage taken from an appraisal and county records - buyer to verify all listing information.
